<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>红烧狮子头</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #FFF9F0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #E67E22;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed #E67E22;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2C3E50;
            margin: 25px 0 15px 0;
            padding-left: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498DB;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            background-color: #FEF6E6;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #F0D9A7;
        }
        li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        li:before {
            content: "•";
            color: #E67E22;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            position: absolute;
            left: 5px;
            top: 6px;
        }
        .step {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3498DB;
            color: white;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 12px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .step-text {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            width: calc(100% - 50px);
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }
        .img-placeholder {
            height: 200px;
            background-color: #ECF0F1;
            border: 2px dashed #BDC3C7;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #7F8C8D;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .step {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .img-placeholder {
                height: 150px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>红烧狮子头</h1>
    
    <h2>所需食材</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>猪绞肉 500克</li>
        <li>荸荠 5-6个</li>
        <li>鸡蛋 1个</li>
        <li>葱姜末 适量</li>
        <li>料酒 1汤匙</li>
        <li>生抽 2汤匙</li>
        <li>老抽 1汤匙</li>
        <li>白糖 1茶匙</li>
        <li>白胡椒粉 少许</li>
        <li>淀粉 适量</li>
        <li>青菜 数棵（装饰用）</li>
        <li>高汤或清水 适量</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>制作步骤</h2>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">1</span>
        <span class="step-text">荸荠去皮切碎，与猪绞肉混合，加入葱姜末、鸡蛋、料酒、生抽（1汤匙）、白胡椒粉和适量淀粉，沿一个方向用力搅拌至肉馅上劲。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：搅拌肉馅]</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">2</span>
        <span class="step-text">将肉馅分成4-6等份，双手沾水，将每份肉馅团成光滑的大肉丸。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：团成肉丸]</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">3</span>
        <span class="step-text">锅中放足量油，烧至六成热，轻轻放入肉丸，中火炸至表面金黄定型后捞出沥油。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：炸制肉丸]</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">4</span>
        <span class="step-text">另起锅，加入少量底油，爆香葱段姜片，倒入高汤或清水，加入剩余的生抽、老抽和白糖，煮沸。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：调制汤汁]</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">5</span>
        <span class="step-text">将炸好的狮子头轻轻放入锅中，汤汁应没过肉丸一半。盖上锅盖，转小火慢炖40-50分钟。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：小火慢炖]</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">6</span>
        <span class="step-text">炖煮期间，将青菜洗净焯水备用。待狮子头炖好后，开大火收汁至汤汁浓稠。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：收汁与焯水青菜]</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="step">
        <span class="step-number">7</span>
        <span class="step-text">将焯好的青菜码放在盘底，小心取出狮子头放在青菜上，最后将浓稠的汤汁淋在狮子头上即可。</span>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：成品摆盘]</div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>